+# Administrative Lens — Current Status
+
+**Status:** Implemented and active for Build workshop & scenario engine.
+
+## Implemented features
+- `data/lego_pieces.json` contains `mapping.mission` entries per piece.
+- `data/ux_labels.json` contains mission labels/icons used by UI.
+- Warehouse seed `warehouse/seeds/plf_2026_plafonds.csv` provides mission ceilings.
+- GraphQL + API: `legoPieces` endpoint surfaces mission metadata.
+- Backward compatibility: COFOG data retained; admin lens default.
+
+## Remaining / planned
+- Parametric estimators for mission-targeted levers (`impact_estimator.py` backlog).
+- Continuous IRF calibration (`data/macro_irfs.json` placeholders).
+
+## Where to look
+- Mission mapping → `data/lego_pieces.json`
+- UX mission labels → `data/ux_labels.json`
+- PLF ceilings seed → `warehouse/seeds/plf_2026_plafonds.csv`
+- dbt project → `warehouse/dbt_project.yml`
+- API → `services/api/data_loader.py`
+
+**Note:** The original detailed checklist lives in `../archive/admin_lens_migration.md`.
